AN important meeting for all taxi owners, drivers and other transporters of pupils is to be held in the Sibongile Hall in Endumeni.This applies to Msinga, Umvoti Nquthu and Endumeni and has been organised by the Umzinyathi Scholars Transport association in conjunction with Santaco. The meeting will take place on Monday 3 July at 10 am and all involved in scholar transport are urged to attend.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.